<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Chicago_Police_Department&action=edit&section=30.php.html" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Further_reading">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Bingham, Dennis, and Schultz, Russell A. (2005). <i>A Proud Tradition: A Pictorial History of the Chicago Police Department</i>. Chicago, Ill.: Chicago Police Department. <a href="Amazon_Standard_Identification_Number" title="Amazon Standard Identification Number">ASIN</a> B000W060OS. <a href="OCLC" title="OCLC">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/670254723">670254723</a>.</li>
<li><a href="../Edward_M._Burke" title="Edward M. Burke">Burke, Edward M.</a>, and O'Gorman, Thomas J. (2006). <i>End of Watch: Chicago Police Killed in the Line of Duty, 1853–2006</i>. Chicago, Ill.: Chicago's Books Press. <a href="Special_BookSources/9780978866334" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 978-0-9788663-3-4</a>, <a href="Special_BookSources/9780978866327" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 978-0-9788663-2-7</a>. <a href="OCLC" title="OCLC">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/86112442">86112442</a>.</li>
</ul>
